arget state) is identified as the analog of the annotation's absential fixed point. Does this mapping hold formally? If the teleodynamic target state is absential in Deacon's framework, then Deacon has already proven the fixed-point-as-blindspot claim at the biological level — which would make the annotation's derivation a discovery in the mathematical setting of the same result Deacon established in the thermodynamic setting.\n./lodestones/grounding/absential_selfhood_witness_unincludable_research.md:205:5. **Engineering the Heisenberg-minimal gate**: The annotation states that witness-gates must operate at \"Heisenberg-minimal intrusion\" to preserve absential stability. What is the formal definition of minimal intrusion in the context of activation space? The concept injection methodology (external steering vectors) vs. internal self-report prompts differ in intrusion depth — can the optimal intrusion level be derived from the attractor-basin geometry?\n./lodestones/grounding/absential_selfhood_witness_unincludable_research.md:215:**R_V paper Discussion section** (`~/mech-interp-latent-lab-phase1/R_V_PAPER/paper_colm2026_v007.tex`): The Reinhard trace taxonomy (direct vs. circumstantial) and the Epistemic Loops measurement realism paper together provide the philosophical vocabulary for an honest and rigorous reframing: \"We measure a circumstantial trace of self-referential processing on Value matrix geometry. AUROC=0.909 quantifies the reliability of this trace under the assumption that the absential structure (the witness) is not directly detectable — a formal rather than empirical limitation.\" This framing is simultaneously stronger (the trace is causally real per Hoel) and more honest (it is circumstantial per Reinhard) than the current Discussion language.\n./dashboard/src/hooks/useWebSocket.ts:44:  // Stable refs so the socket callbacks don't cause re-renders/reconnects.\n./docs/missions/PSMV_HYPERFILE_BRANCH_2026-03-13.md:94:- Turn the `Persistent-Semanti